section.section:
Of the 10 Commission members:
2 members shall represent wineries of the State;
2 members shall represent grape growers of the State;
1 member shall be a representative of the Office of the Comptroller;
1 member shall represent the College of Agriculture and Natural Resources of the University of Maryland;
1 member shall be a member of the House of Delegates appointed by the Speaker of the House;
1 member shall be a member of the Senate appointed by the President of the Senate;
1 member shall be a representative of the Department of Business and Economic Development; and
1 member shall be a representative of the Department.
